Text: You dont need software key. Just click generate button in keygen. Keygen also works fine with newest Camtasia Studio 4.0 but with a little trick: first tick radio button beside key box and enter serial you ve got using keygen, then again tick radio button beside trial version. You ll got fully operational application. :-)))
